罗比·威廉姆斯 (Robbie Williams) 谈与 Oasis 同期巡演时：“这不是一场比赛，尽管它确实是一场比赛” https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-touring-at-the-same-time-as-oasis-its-not-a-competition-even-though-it-bloody- is-3812698?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=罗比·威廉姆斯在绿洲同一时间巡演，尽管它是血腥的，但它不是比赛Alex RigottiThu, 14 Nov 2024 12:37:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3812698 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗比·威廉姆斯和利亚姆·加拉格尔（布莱恩·拉西克/盖蒂图片社拍摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “绿洲回归，我认为没有人可以与之竞争——包括泰勒·斯威夫特”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-on-touring-at-the-same-time-as-oasis-its-not-a-competition-even-though-it-bloody-is-3812698">罗比·威廉姆斯（Robbie Williams）关于与 Oasis 同时巡演的帖子：“这不是一场比赛，尽管它是血腥的”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗比·威廉姆斯和利亚姆·加拉格尔（摄影：Brian Rasic/Getty Images）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Robbie-Williams-Liam-Gallagher-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>复出巡演的同时公开谈论了巡演。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552"><strong> </strong>支持我：2025年绿洲阵容中所有可能的球员</a></strong></li></ul><p>就在几天前（11 月 11 日），这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">Take That</a>明星宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-2025-uk-ireland-europe-tour-buy-tickets-3811519#:~:text=Robbie%20Williams%20has%20announced%20details,Find%20ticket%20details%20below.&amp;text=The%20pop%20icon%20and%20former,in%20Edinburgh%20on%20May%2031.">他 2025 年英国、爱尔兰和欧洲巡演的一系列日期</a>。威廉姆斯将于 5 月 31 日在爱丁堡开始比赛，并一直持续到 9 月。</p><p>在此之前，Oasis <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">自己的重聚巡演</a>的消息传出，他们去年八月宣布回归，此前几周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-oasis-reuniting-for-huge-london-and-manchester-shows-3786823">有报道称英伦流行巨头将回归</a>，利亚姆<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-oasis-reunion-noel-3787153">在他的雷丁节头条节目中调侃了这次重聚</a>。这将是他们自 2009 年乐队解散以来的首场演出。</p><p>现在，罗比·威廉姆斯已经回应了他计划巡回演出与绿洲竞争的建议。在 Instagram 上发布的一段采访片段中，威廉姆斯回答道：“不，我没有。</p><p> “当绿洲重新团结起来时，真的就没有竞争了，”他继续说道。 “除非我休息 20 年，否则这将是一场公平的战斗。绿洲回归，我认为没有人可以与之竞争——包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>，他是这个星球上最伟大的艺术家。所以不，这不是一场比赛，尽管它确实是一场比赛。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DCUjpakAUd3/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106